_sText:
This is the first map I have ever made and I was hoping by posting it on here I could get some feedback, I realize I don't have very good screenshots atm unfortunately so I guess you'll just have to check it out yourself :P

The map starts off like any ordinary texture / aim map but with scouts, only eventually you will find a teleporter that you can use to go way up high where you can find awps! :O, from there on its filled with teleporters, ladders and guns as you get higher and higher up until finally you reach a place where you can get any gun you want as well as lots of nades.

If you would like to contact me add my xfire: darksoul616

P.S. I realize this map isn't great to the eyes... With no lighting etc. But I made it for fun, not so you could oggle over good graphics.
